title: Renegade 14-Gauge Round Point Caprock Irrigation Shovel with 47 in. Ash Wood Handle
description: After 35 years, Hisco's mission continues to focus on providing our customers the highest quality professional grade hand tools. The Renegade 14-Gauge Round Point Caprock Irrigation Shovel works in shallow channels and is extremely tough for withstanding many years of use on the farm or jobsite.
